welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Ellensburg, the charming city known for its beautiful surroundings, rich culture, and friendly locals. We invite you to explore our quaint downtown, scenic hiking trails, and delicious local cuisine. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bowers Field Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Bowers Field Airport handles all freight and cargo shipments.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Yakima Air Terminal serves all commercial flights and offers a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Yakima Air Terminal is primarily used for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the terminal.
